dustrial relations/employment law; and 4. Intellectual property. Each advanced topic will take about two hours to cover. Bearing in mind that it will be quite a lot to take in we would recommend that there be a 15 minute break in the middle of each topic and a more substantial break between topics. We would prefer to deliver two to three standard length sessions during a single day. It might be possible to deliver all four in one day, in a condensed form, but that format has a greater risk of information overload and disengagement. Please contact Stephen Cardona for more information 0499 772 021 or info@ntibn.com.au\r\n\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:30:\"LEGAL WORKSHOP By Marrawah Law\";s:12:\"post_excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:13:\"post_password\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"post_name\";s:30:\"legal-workshop-by-marrawah-law\";s:7:\"to_ping\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"pinged\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"post_modified\";s:19:\"2019-12-28 22:46:28\";s:17:\"post_modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2019-12-28 17:46:28\";s:21:\"post_content_filtered\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_parent\";i:0;s:4:\"guid\";s:65:\"http://127.0.0.1/ntibn-wp/web/?post_type=event_listing&#038;p=179\";s:10:\"menu_order\";i:0;s:9:\"post_type\";s:13:\"event_listing\";s:14:\"post_mime_type\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"comment_count\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}}s:10:\"post_count\";i:1;s:12:\"current_post\";i:-1;s:11:\"in_the_loop\";b:0;s:4:\"post\";r:107;s:13:\"comment_count\";i:0;s:15:\"current_comment\";i:-1;s:11:\"found_posts\";s:1:\"1\";s:13:\"max_num_pages\";d:1;s:21:\"max_num_comment_pages\";i:0;s:9:\"is_single\";b:0;s:10:\"is_preview\";b:0;s:7:\"is_page\";b:0;s:10:\"is_archive\";b:0;s:7:\"is_date\";b:0;s:7:\"is_year\";b:0;s:8:\"is_month\";b:0;s:6:\"is_day\";b:0;s:7:\"is_time\";b:0;s:9:\"is_author\";b:0;s:11:\"is_category\";b:0;s:6:\"is_tag\";b:0;s:6:\"is_tax\";b:0;s:9:\"is_search\";b:0;s:7:\"is_feed\";b:0;s:15:\"is_comment_feed\";b:0;s:12:\"is_trackb