(14, 1, '2019-12-04 15:50:56', '2019-12-04 10:50:56', '<h3>Membership</h3>		\n		<p>Members of the NTIBN have access to a wide range of services and benefits within the network. These include</p>\n<ul style=\'margin:0;\'>\n 	<li>Access to the peak body representing NT Indigenous business</li>\n 	<li>Organisational development for NT Indigenous business</li>\n 	<li>Industry based development for NT Indigenous business</li>\n 	<li>Member business support</li>\n 	<li>Collaborative and promotion opportunities</li>\n 	<li>Training and personal development to support current and emerging business</li>\n 	<li>Regional representatives and support for remote business operators</li>\n</ul>		\n																	<img src=\"http://127.0.0.1/ntibn-wp/web/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/membership.png\" alt=\"\">\n	                        <h2>Certified Membership</h2>\n	                           <p></p>\n	                        <h2>Certified Membership</h2>\n	                           <p><p>Certified Membership are for businesses that are a minimum of 51% Indigenous owned, has majority Indigenous control and is a Northern Territory based business. Confirmation of Aboriginality or cultural identity is a requirement of the certification process. Statutory declarations are not accepted.</p></p>\n																	<img src=\"http://127.0.0.1/ntibn-wp/web/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/membership.png\" alt=\"\">\n	                        <h2>Associate Membership</h2>\n	                           <p></p>\n	                        <h2>Associate Membership</h2>\n	                           <p><p>Associate Membership is for any business that does not meet the criteria for Certified membership, that supports Indigenous business and/or Indigenous employment.</p></p>\n			<a href=\"http://127.0.0.1/ntibn-wp/web/register.php\" role=\"button\">\n						Join Us\n					</a>', 'Membership', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'membership', '', '', '2019-12-26 12:55:52', '2019-12-26 07:55:52', '', 0, 'http://127.0.0.1/ntibn-wp/?page_id=14', 0, 'page', '', 0),
