ritage. Ray is the director of DICE Australia and associated companies which include Dice Contracting, Dice Renascent and Alpha Dice.</p></p>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-12-05 12:45:06', '2019-12-05 07:45:06', '', 12, 'http://127.0.0.1/ntibn-wp/12-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
