(148, 1, '2019-12-05 18:24:05', '2019-12-05 13:24:05', '<h3>Membership</h3>		\n		<p>Members of the NTIBN have access to a wide range of services and benefits within the network. These include</p><ul><li>Access to the peak body representing NT Indigenous business</li><li>Organisational development for NT Indigenous business</li><li>Industry based development for NT Indigenous business</li><li>Member business support</li><li>Collaborative and promotion opportunities</li><li>Training and personal development to support current and emerging business</li><li>Regional representatives and support for remote business operators</li></ul>		\n	                        <h2>Certified Membership</h2>\n	                           <p></p>\n	                        <h2>Certified Membership</h2>\n	                           <p><p>Certified Membership are for businesses that are a minimum of 51% Indigenous owned, has majority Indigenous control and is a Northern Territory based business. Confirmation of Aboriginality or cultural identity is a requirement of the certification process. Statutory declarations are not accepted.</p></p>\n	                        <h2>Associate Membership</h2>\n	                           <p></p>\n	                        <h2>Associate Membership</h2>\n	                           <p><p>Associate Membership is for any business that does not meet the criteria for Certified membership, that supports Indigenous business and/or Indigenous employment.</p></p>\n			<a href=\"http://127.0.0.1/ntibn-wp/web/register.php\" role=\"button\">\n						Join Us\n					</a>', 'Membership', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '14-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-12-05 18:24:05', '2019-12-05 13:24:05', '', 14, 'http://127.0.0.1/ntibn-wp/web/14-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
