(179, 1, '2019-12-18 10:34:20', '2019-12-18 05:34:20', 'Start Date : January 23 2020\r\n\r\nEnd Date : January 23 2020\r\n\r\nTicket Price: $10\r\n\r\nMembers Price : $10\r\n\r\nBasic workshops cover legal essentials for small business. This workshop runs for about two hours and covers, at a very high level, wills and powers of attorney, partnering in business, IP, business premises (including zoning and leasing), risk management (including consumer protection, contracts and debt recovery), human resources and business compliance. Our firm is in the process of developing advanced workshops for Indigenous businesses and organisations on four topics: 1. Joint ventures and partnerships; 2. Contract negotiations; 3. Industrial relations/employment law; and 4. Intellectual property. Each advanced topic will take about two hours to cover. Bearing in mind that it will be quite a lot to take in we would recommend that there be a 15 minute break in the middle of each topic and a more substantial break between topics. We would prefer to deliver two to three standard length sessions during a single day. It might be possible to deliver all four in one day, in a condensed form, but that format has a greater risk of information overload and disengagement. Please contact Stephen Cardona for more information 0499 772 021 or info@ntibn.com.au\r\n', 'LEGAL WORKSHOP By Marrawah Law', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'legal-workshop-by-marrawah-law', '', '', '2019-12-28 22:46:28', '2019-12-28 17:46:28', '', 0, 'http://127.0.0.1/ntibn-wp/web/?post_type=event_listing&#038;p=179', 0, 'event_listing', '', 0),
